                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/10214" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1509</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">305 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">白金宿突围：安吉阿忠的家民宿网络营销的破局之道</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Breakthrough of Platinum Inn: Anji Azhong&#39;s Home Homestay Network Marketing Breakthrough</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">徐清，蔡粤韦，彭雨婷</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安吉灵峰青梨民宿旅店</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文化、体育和娱乐业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小微型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">网络营销；4C理论；阿忠的家；乡村民宿</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Online marketing; 4C theory ;Ah Zhong&#39;s home; Rural homestays</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了在民宿行业低迷时期，浙江安吉“阿忠的家”白金宿通过网络营销策略实现逆势增长的过程。首先，“阿忠的家”在面对疫情后大量订单和顾客流失的困境时，抓住了新媒体的快速发展为各行各业带来的流量和机遇，明确了自身的优势和“阿忠的家”的目标客户。在抖音、小红书、微信视频号等平台，根据不同平台用户的特色，投放宣传视频和推文，并且在抖音平台定期直播宣传。由此，“阿忠的家”成功以低成本收获了一大批忠实顾客，成功克服了市场变化给民宿发展带来的困境。本案例通过分析“阿忠的家”在4C理论指导下的网络营销实践过程，引导学生思考乡村民宿在现有资源条件下，如何运用4C理论的基本要素、驱动因素、核心价值以及沟通策略进行网络营销破局，从而增强市场竞争力和复购率，突破同质化困境，激活乡村民宿活力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes the online marketing strategy of &quot;Ah Zhong&#39;s Home&quot; in Anji, Zhejiang Province, to realize growth against the trend during the downturn of the homestay industry. First of all, &quot;Ah Zhong&#39;s Home&quot;, in the face of the plight of a large number of orders and loss of customers after the epidemic, seized the traffic and opportunities brought by the rapid development of new media, and clarified its own strengths and &quot;Ah Zhong&#39;s Home&quot; target customers, and then Tiktok, Xiaohongshu and Weibo to promote its products and services to the public. It put promotional videos and tweets on platforms such as Tiktok, Xiaohongshu and WeChat according to the characteristics of users on different platforms, and regularly broadcast live promotions on the Tiktok. As a result, &quot;Ah Zhong&#39;s Home&quot; has successfully gained a large number of loyal customers at a low cost, and successfully overcome the difficulties brought by market changes to the development of homestay industry. This case analyzes the online marketing practice of &quot;Ah Zhong&#39;s Home&quot; under the guidance of the 4C theory, and guides students to think about how to use the basic elements of the 4C theory, driving factors, core values, and communication strategies to break through online marketing under the existing resources, so as to enhance the competitiveness of the market and the rate of repurchase, and to break through the homogenization dilemma and activate the development of rural lodgings. Break through the homogenization dilemma and activate the vitality of rural homestay industry. </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">4C理论的内涵及基本要素；4C理论执行的驱动因素；4C理论的核心价值；以消费者为中心的网络营销沟通策略</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-12</td>
                            </tr>
